survey_response.review_text: Dr. Rashmi is an absolute gem in the dental field! Their expertise and attention to detail are unparalleled. Not only did they address my dental concerns with precision, but they also took the time to ensure I felt comfortable throughout the entire process. Their friendly demeanor and genuine care for their patients truly set them apart. I couldn't be happier with the results of my visit and highly recommend to anyone in need of top-notch dental care.

The doctor is quite friendly and understands your problems very well. Also educates you about your issues and explains the way forward. Patients are not kept waiting for long time due to good time management. The ambience of the clinic is good. I would definitely refer my friends and acquaintance to this clinic. Keep up the good work of taking care of your patients

Dr. Rashmi Shetty at K.K. Memorial Dental Center is an exceptional dentist who provided me with outstanding care. I have been treated for four extractions and multiple composite fillings from her, and I am extremely satisfied with the results. Dr. Shetty's friendly and personable demeanour immediately put me at ease during each visit.

Her skill and expertise were evident as she performed the extractions and fillings with precision and care. Despite the complexity of the procedures, Dr. Shetty ensured that I experienced minimal discomfort throughout. Her ability to perform these treatments painlessly showcases her exceptional skills and dedication to patient comfort.

Dr. Rashmi Shetty's approachable nature and willingness to listen to my concerns and answer my questions made each visit a positive experience. She took the time to explain the procedures, providing me with a clear understanding of what to expect. This level of communication and patient involvement is a testament to her commitment to delivering personalized care.

The modern and up-to-date facility at K.K. Memorial Dental Center further enhanced my experience. The entire staff was welcoming, and the atmosphere was comfortable and calming. I appreciated the high level of professionalism exhibited by Dr. Shetty and her team.
Dr explained the procedure in detail and the precautions to be taken post the implant. Gave valuable suggestions for future problems.

I consulted Dr. Rashmi for wisdom tooth extraction and cavity filling. All the dental appointments were very smooth and I never had to wait long at the clinic. Dr. Rashmi offered me honest medical advice and explained my dental issues to me in detail. She was always available to answer any queries I had about my treatment. The oral surgeon was very competent and extracted my wisdom teeth within 10-15 minutes on each occasion.  Doctor's assistants are also very helpful and follow up diligently for any issues you may face and help manage the smooth running of the clinic. I consulted Dr. Rashmi on a recommendation and I would in turn like to recommend her for resolving any dental issues you may have.

Doctor Rashmi Shetty and her team of assistants is very friendly. Doctor Rashmi and her team conducts treatment in excellent manner. They have maintained cleanliness and ambience of the Dental clinic. I had gone to Doctor for removal of a milk tooth's residue and Dental Crown, it felt like a rebirth for the tooth. There was a time when I was very scared Doctor Rashmi and her team helped me calm down when I felt relaxed thats when the task was done and I felt very happy. As for the dental crown I am very happy. 
Doctor Rashmi does the task very carefully as a result my Dental crown has been a great success.

Extremely happy and satisfied with the care and treatment that I got from Dr Shetty, Dr Yash and Dr Sakshi. They were really polite and explained the entire treatment to me in layman’s term. They ensured that the pain subsides immediately. The entire team is really punctual and cares a lot about their patients. Even after my RCT treatment, the doctors took followups just to check with me if there is no pain and I’m not facing any issues. Will 10/10 recommend Dr Shetty and team for a one stop solution for all dental needs.

Firstly the dental clinic is pleasingly decorated & the ambience is nice. Support staff are helpful & follow-up & reminder for appointments is good. There is no clubbing of patients & no rush. The doctor & all the other dentists take pain to customize the treatment for each individual taking into consideration all the factors. They explain everything in detail & clarify all doubts. The cost of treatment is very reasonable & totally value for money. The dentists and doctors have very pleasing personalities which is a big plus. I would recommend people to try it out.

Dr Rashmi is very professional at her work ..On my regular check up with her she realised that my wisdom tooth needed to be extracted  . I was very skeptical of doing the surgery but thanks to her reassurance she made me feel comfortable . She explained the whole procedure to me and the after care to be taken . The surgery was conducted in her clinic by a visting Surgent  who was very professional too  he explained me each stage of the procedure while Dr Rashmi was present through the surgery . After the surgery Dr Rashmi checked on me by calling me and and also answered all my queries that I had during the recovery .
Even her staff in her clinic are very friendly and polite .
People say wisdom tooth extraction is so traumatic but for me it was such a smooth experience thanks to Dr Rashmi and her staff. Thank you once again .

Do not trust them. I had gone to Dr. Yoban for braces consultation during which I also asked him to check if my teeth are healthy. He told me I need to get fillings done. So I went ahead with it. 
Dr. Rashmi was supposed to do my fillings but she made her intern/assistant do the work and didn't even bother to supervise it. At the moment I trusted everything but after getting the filling done I had pain for a month. I visited again for the pain and they told me that it's for some other reason which they've now fixed. I still had a lot of pain so I got it checked by someone else *** ***** *** **** ** ***** *** ***** * **** ***** ******* *** ******* ** ******** *** ***** *** ***** *** **** ******* **** **** ** *** ******** ***
I had no issues or pain when I first went to see them for braces. But now I'm getting a root canal done out of nowhere.

Not to forget, during the process i got injured on my lips too because the machine got stuck on it and she couldn't even notice until I raised my hand and stopped her.

Eventually I did not even go back to them for braces.

My molar teeth were in a very bad state, but Dr. Shetty made every effort to save them, explaining the reasons for extraction and addressing all my concerns with genuine care and understanding. The extraction and implant process went seamlessly and without any pain, demonstrating her remarkable expertise and unwavering commitment to my well-being. I was deeply impressed by Dr. Shetty's dedication to ensuring my comfort throughout the entire treatment, and her exceptional post-treatment care left me feeling secure and well-cared for during my recovery. Not only did Dr. Shetty provide a flawless implant result, but she also fully restored my trust in dental procedures. For anyone seeking exceptional dental care with a personal touch, I wholeheartedly recommend Dr. Rashmi Shetty.
